snippet.title: PCEngine : Tricky (1991)
snippet.description:
Secret Special Game Clear.
Input password "MILKYWAY" and push II buttun two times, so It starts the Secret Special Game.
Special Game is very hard. There are no easy stages. 

This is long-time movie Encode TEST.
